window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A collection of true paranormal stories that’ll have you sleeping with one eye open...</b></p> <p>This anthology details encounters with ghosts, evil spirits, dark entities, malicious beings, and demonic encounters that’ll send a chill of terror tickling up your spine. Don’t worry, you’re not alone. There’s almost certainly a ghost or two peeking over your shoulder. These true paranormal encounters are unlike any you’ve heard before. And, if you don’t believe, just know that you don’t have to believe in something for it to exist.</p> <p>This anthology makes a great gift for the horror fan in your life, perfect for the storyteller that loves to scare others around a campfire, or for anyone who thinks ghosts aren’t real - prepare to listen to some of the darkest true stories ever recorded.</p>"; 
